data.description:
Welcome to Ponte Vedra Beach’s newest outdoor sports and social venue. The Yards is an innovative reimagining of the traditional country club. The first of its kind in the region, The Yards features a completely renovated and redesigned 12-hole golf course, tennis center, and brand new pickleball facility, The Pickle Garden. In addition to the sports facilities, The Yards also has a covered patio pavilion overlooking the beautiful course that is perfect for any occasion, as well as another multi-purpose event space coming in 2024. The Yards welcomes members, their guests, and visitors from all across the country to come enjoy the greater Ponte Vedra area and all it has to offer. Play The Yards!

Stay in the know! Follow @playtheyards on
- Instagram
- Facebook
- TikTok
- YouTube

Subscribe to our mailing list here: http://eepurl.com/heZ9QT
